    "L2 writers might have a narrower range of vocabulary and less fluency compared to L1 writers, which could result in a stronger focus on familiar and concrete topics, such as leadership and health, and a greater reliance on real-world experiences and current events.",
    "This contrasts with ChatGPT-3.5, which has access to vast database of information and can generate content on a wide range of topics, including more abstract or technical themes.",
