    "The horizontal axis represents the association strength (Log OR), while the vertical axis lists the keywords.",
    "Each point on the chart corresponds to a specific keyword and its Log OR value, indicating the frequency and importance of that keyword in L2 human-generated content compared to GPTgenerated content."
